iled to hr vmi edu to meet the deadline  However  original materials must follow by mail or in person  State guidelines require our office to have a state application with original signature on file  Applications must be received in our office by 4 30 p m  on the deadline  Postmarks will not be honored  Select positions are now accepting online applications through the Virginia State Job Site  Instructions for creating an account and applying to positions are included in the link  These position postings will include a hyperlink to the site and specify that online applications are accepted  You can also use this site to complete the state application and print for positions not yet accepting online applications Human Resources Employment Opportunities How to Apply Virginia Jobs Website Benefits   Services For Employees Training Policies HR Forms Staff Inclement Weather Policy Fraud  Waste   Abuse Hotline P   540  464 7322 F   540  464 7299  E  hroffice vmi edu Human Resources Office Virginia Military Institute 305 Letcher Avenue Lexington  VA 24450  Human Resources Employment Opportunities How to Apply Virginia Jobs Website Benefits   Services For Employees Training Policies HR Forms Staff Inclement Weather Policy Fraud  Waste   Abuse Hotline P   540  464 7322 F   540  464 7299  E  hroffice vmi edu Human Resources Office Virginia Military Institute 305 Letcher Avenue Lexington  VA 24450 Human Resources Employment Opportunities How to Apply Virginia Jobs Website Benefits   Services For Employees Training Policies HR Forms Staff Human Resources Human Resources Employment Opportunities How to Apply Virginia Jobs Website Employment Opportunities Employment Opportunities How to Apply Virginia Jobs Website How to Apply How to Apply How to Apply Virginia Jobs Website Virginia Jobs Website Benefits   Services Benefits   Services For Employees For Employees Training Training Policies Policies HR Forms HR Forms Staff Staff Inclement Weather Policy Fraud  Waste   Abuse Hotline